        Conversations track in Barcelona, and acted as Global Track Chair for Core Conversations at DrupalCon Dublin
        2016 and DrupalCon Vienna 2017.
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="speaker">
      <img class="speaker--picture" src="/{{ directory }}/images/speakers/marcos.jpg" alt="Marcos Cano">
      <span class="speaker--session">Flujos de contenido estructurado en Drupal</span>
      <span class ="speaker--bio">
